		<defName>AC_FilledArchotechStack</defName>
		<label>archo stack</label>
		<description>An archotech cortical implant with a human consciousness stored on it, commonly referred to as a persona. Can be implanted directly into a person's or sleeveâ€™s spine in the neck to bring back the person stored on the stack.</description>
